<br>
If you join a group and don’t ask what the looting rules were, you have no right to be upset with the warrior when he claims the Codpiece of Hammering.<br>
<br>
I asked to join a group once and was invited in.  The looting rules were “everything goes to [Frank].”  The reasons that Frank got to loot everything were many and varied, and they have no real bearing on this thread.<br>
<br>
I agreed.  I didn’t particularly like the rules as I was a bit short of cash, but they were the only group willing to take me and I didn’t relish hiking to another zone or trying to solo.<br>
<br>
